- Do not use await inside loops whener is possible. 
- Do not use await without try catch
- Do not track your code using if and elses or try catches unecessarily.
- Give only one responsability to a function whenever is possible. Is easier to test your code. 
- Try to not use arrow functions, use Function expressions, is much readble. 
- Are there any methods that could be replaced as language methods as Array.map(), filter(), Object.create()...?
- Could you use a factory function? 
- Could you use a constructor function?
- Is not better use a Class, for exemplo to validation chained? 
